@SleepHQImporter_HostAddress = http://localhost:5175
@apiKey = your-api-key-here

### Upload a ZIP file to SleepHQ
POST {{SleepHQImporter_HostAddress}}/api/shortcuts/upload
X-Uplink-ApiKey: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----Boundary

------Boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sleep-data.zip"
Content-Type: application/zip

< ./sample-data.zip
------Boundary--

###
